# Frontend Rules (Auto)

- All API calls go through a single apiClient:
  - apiBase = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE ?? ""
  - default same-origin; dev uses Vite proxy
- Mode stored only as UPPER in state. Normalize at boundaries.
- No magic layout constants like right: 380px.
  - Use CSS vars: --chat-w, --drawer-max-h (38vh).
- HUD must show truth (no UNKNOWN). If data missing -> explicit empty/partial state.
- Backtest drawer reads from app state (job_id/status/result). No window events.
